REM Title: Cowsay fortune
REM Author: Cypher
REM Description: Pipes a random fortune through cowsay. Falls back to plain
REM echo if neither tool is installed.
REM Target: macOS (`brew install cowsay fortune` for best results)
DELAY 500
GUI SPACE
DELAY 500
STRING Terminal
DELAY 1000
ENTER
DELAY 800
STRING (fortune 2>/dev/null || echo "moo.") | (cowsay 2>/dev/null || cat)
ENTER
